鱐字的基本解释

sù
干鱼：“夏行腒鱐，膳膏臊。”

鱐字的汉语字典释义

[①]［sù］
［《廣韻》息逐切，入屋，心。］
亦作“1”。
(1)干鱼。
(2)鱼名。

鱐字的康熙字典解释

【亥集中】【魚字部】　鱐； 康熙笔画：23； 页码：页1478第09
【廣韻】息逐切【集韻】息六切，?音肅。魚腊。【周禮·天官·庖人】夏行腒鱐。【疏】鱐謂乾魚。【禮·內則】夏宜腒鱐。【釋文】鱐，本又作鱐。又【集韻】思留切，音脩。義同。

Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words
[Hai Collection] [Fish Character Department] 　鱐; Kangxi Strokes: 23; Page Number: Page 1478 Page 09
[Guang Yun] Breathing and cutting [Jiyun] Breathing in six cuttings, sound and su. Fish wax. 【Zhou Li·Tian Guan·Bo Ren】Xia Xing Fu. [Sparse] 鱐 is dried fish. 【Rite·Nei Ze】Xia Yifuya. 【Explanation】Qi, this is also called 鱐. Also 【Jiyun】Thinking to keep cutting, sound repairing. The same meaning.
